      "span_text": "Validation for low frequency variants was performed by high-resolution melt (HRM) analysis on a Rotor-Gene Q (Qiagen), before and after uracil-DNA glycosylase (UDG) treatment to control for FFPE sequence artifacts as previously described [CITATION_1] ."
